      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Evening Sun</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>when they saw you in the evening sunno one thought that you could be someone </l>
          <l>but you belong </l>
          <l>to those who won the game </l>
          <l>just the day to watch my sister goes </l>
          <l>just the day to watch this dream explodes </l>
          <l>you must be real </l>
          <l>you must be real </l>
          <l>to me </l>
          <l>now, looking at the sky </l>
          <l>the morning moon keeps you safe </l>
          <l>inside the raging sea </l>
          <l>and you had it all </l>
          <l>yes you had it all </l>
          <l>before me </l>
          <l>before me</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
